"adding-liked-youtube-videos-to-a-spotify-playlist\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e2 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Adding liked YouTube videos to a Spotify playlist\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"get-your-streaming-services-to-work-together\"\u003e\n            Get your streaming services to work together\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eWhile most of my IFTTT applets are custom creations, this one is one created by Google. If you use both YouTube and Spotify, you can get IFTTT to create a Spotify playlist based on videos you like on YouTube.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eI find this specific automation useful because Spotify and YouTube often recommend different songs to me. YouTube\u0026#39;s recommendations are more based on the rock songs I enjoy, while Spotify suggests a lot more general alternative music. But I only watch music videos on YouTube; I don\u0026#39;t use it for general music streaming.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWith the IFTTT applet, I can bring the two services together when I\u0026#39;m browsing music videos. That said, the right songs will only populate on Spotify if the song is available on the service. I found that accuracy definitely varies, with some strange songs popping up on my Spotify playlist.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"8acf-411b-8811dcece3a7\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/power-automate-is-the-ultimate-automation-tool-for-windows/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"6000\" height=\"3376\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A Windows 11 laptop running RoboTask and Power Automate\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-robotask-and-power-automate.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/power-automate-is-the-ultimate-automation-tool-for-windows/\" title=\"5 reasons Power Automate is the ultimate automation tool for Windows\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\t5 reasons Power Automate is the ultimate automation tool for Windows\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003ePower Automate allows you to run time-sucking  repetitive tasks automatically. Through automation, you can boost productivity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"sending-free-game-deals-to-discord\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e1 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Sending free game deals to Discord\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"a-reddit-based-automation\"\u003e\n            A Reddit-based automation\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eThere are a variety of ways to get notifications for free games, including following certain subreddits. IFTTT has existing applets for getting free game notifications, but I found that they were either platform-specific (i.e. only Steam games) or included all games that are free-to-play.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAs a result, I set up a Reddit trigger on IFTTT that searches a specific subreddit (r/GameDeals) for new posts with the term \u0026#34;free game\u0026#34;. Once IFTTT picks up a new post meeting the search terms, it will send a message to my personal Discord server.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"1ae7-467a-86e69b7214eb\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/must-have-productivity-tools-remote-workers/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003