ith-widget-launcher.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-laptop-with-widget-launcher.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-laptop-with-widget-launcher.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-laptop-with-widget-launcher.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-laptop-with-widget-launcher.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"6000\" height=\"3376\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A Windows 11 laptop with various widgets on the desktop powered by Widget Launcher\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-laptop-with-widget-launcher.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/02/windows-11-laptop-with-widget-launcher.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/must-have-productivity-tools-remote-workers/\" title=\"7 must-have productivity tools for remote workers\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\t7 must-have productivity tools for remote workers\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThe must-have apps for remote working include communication and project management tools, among others. I picked the best for you!\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"ifttt-has-a-variety-of-niche-automations\"\u003e\n            IFTTT has a variety of niche automations\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you use IFTTT, I recommend trying out custom applets with supported services to see what types of tasks you can automate. The platform is relatively beginner-friendly and you can even take existing applets and edit them according to your needs. The biggest drawback, however, is that IFTTT\u0026#39;s free plan only supports two concurrent applets. If you want something with more free features, \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/huginn-free-open-source-ifttt-alternative/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eHuginn is a free and open-source alternative to IFTTT\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                                \n        \n                            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ifttt-logo.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;Source: IFTTT\u0026#34;\" data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"76a0-419a-b34a8646c6b7\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ifttt-logo.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=480\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ifttt-logo.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=480\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                            